    Start([üë®‚Äçüíª New Contributor<br/>Ready to Help]) --> Step1

    subgraph Setup["Step 1: Setup (15 min)"]
        Step1[Fork & Clone Repository]
        Step1 --> Install[Install Dependencies<br/>pip install -e .[dev]]
        Install --> Configure[Configure Pre-commit Hooks<br/>pre-commit install]
        Configure --> Verify[make test<br/>Verify All Tests Pass]
    end

    subgraph Choose["Step 2: Choose Contribution Type"]
        Verify --> Choice{What Type of<br/>Contribution?}
        Choice -->|Bug Fix| Bug[Fix Bug]
        Choice -->|Feature| Feature[Add Feature]
        Choice -->|Docs| Docs[Improve Docs]
        Choice -->|Test| Test[Add Tests]
        Choice -->|Refactor| Refactor[Refactor Code]
    end

    subgraph Development["Step 3: Development"]
        Bug --> Branch[Create Feature Branch<br/>git checkout -b feature/xyz]
        Feature --> Branch
        Docs --> Branch
        Test --> Branch
        Refactor --> Branch

        Branch --> Code[Write Code & Tests]
        Code --> Lint[make lint<br/>Run Linters]
        Lint --> TestLocal[make test<br/>Run All Tests]
    end

    subgraph Validation["Step 4: Validation"]
        TestLocal --> Quality{Quality Checks}
        Quality -->|Lint Error| FixLint[Fix Linting Issues]
        Quality -->|Test Failure| FixTest[Fix Test Failures]
        Quality -->|All Pass| Ready

        FixLint --> Code
        FixTest --> Code
    end

    subgraph Submit["Step 5: Submit PR"]
        Ready[Commit Changes<br/>git commit -m 'feat: add X'] --> Push[Push to Fork<br/>git push origin feature/xyz]
        Push --> CreatePR[Create Pull Request<br/>On GitHub]
        CreatePR --> Fill[Fill PR Template<br/>- Description<br/>- Testing<br/>- Checklist]
    end

    subgraph Review["Step 6: Review & Merge"]
        Fill --> CI[CI/CD Checks<br/>- Tests<br/>- Lint<br/>- Security Scan]
        CI --> Checks{All Checks<br/>Pass?}
        Checks -->|No| FixPR[Address Feedback<br/>& Update PR]
        Checks -->|Yes| Review[Code Review<br/>by Maintainers]
        Review --> Approved{Approved?}
        Approved -->|No| FixPR
        Approved -->|Yes| Merge[Merge PR<br/>& Delete Branch]
        FixPR --> CI
    end

    Merge --> Celebrate([üéâ Contribution<br/>Merged!])

